00:08:37.690 --> 00:08:41.559 align:middle line:84%
And the answer to that is that
fluids in their natural state

00:08:41.559 --> 00:08:45.080 align:middle line:84%
want to move-- in the ground,
water, and in our bodies,

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:47.860 align:middle line:84%
blood-- will move
of its own volition

00:08:47.860 --> 00:08:50.680 align:middle line:84%
through what are called little
micro vortices, little spirals

00:08:50.680 --> 00:08:51.480 align:middle line:90%
of motion.

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:55.350 align:middle line:84%
The heart helps, but it will
move without the heart pumping.

00:08:55.350 --> 00:08:57.660 align:middle line:84%
So that leads to the
question that Bremer asked.

00:08:57.660 --> 00:09:00.240 align:middle line:84%
If this is happening
without the heart,

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:02.240 align:middle line:84%
maybe the primary
purpose of the heart

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:04.660 align:middle line:84%
is more than simply
pumping blood?

00:09:04.660 --> 00:09:09.570 align:middle line:84%
What else does our heart do
that we have yet to explore?

00:09:09.570 --> 00:09:12.420 align:middle line:84%
And part of the answer to
that was discovered in 1991.

00:09:12.420 --> 00:09:16.580 align:middle line:84%
In 1991, scientists
found in the human heart

00:09:16.580 --> 00:09:21.430 align:middle line:84%
a collection of a little over
40,000 specialized cells called

00:09:21.430 --> 00:09:24.110 align:middle line:84%
sensory neurites,
which is a very

00:09:24.110 --> 00:09:27.100 align:middle line:84%
fancy word for brain-like cells,
but they're not in the brain.

00:09:27.100 --> 00:09:29.990 align:middle line:84%
They're in the heart, a
neural network in the heart.

00:09:29.990 --> 00:09:33.320 align:middle line:84%
And these neurons,
they are so brain-like,

00:09:33.320 --> 00:09:35.330 align:middle line:84%
they can actually
remember independent

00:09:35.330 --> 00:09:36.240 align:middle line:90%
of the cranial brain.

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:39.020 align:middle line:84%
They can think independently
of the cranial brain.

00:09:39.020 --> 00:09:41.140 align:middle line:84%
They can feel and
sense independently

00:09:41.140 --> 00:09:42.520 align:middle line:90%
of the cranial brain.

00:09:42.520 --> 00:09:43.550 align:middle line:90%
So there's one path.

00:09:43.550 --> 00:09:46.830 align:middle line:84%
What is it that our hearts are
capable of that we are only

00:09:46.830 --> 00:09:48.200 align:middle line:90%
beginning to understand?

00:09:48.200 --> 00:09:51.130 align:middle line:84%
Number two, as it
applies to my experience,

00:09:51.130 --> 00:09:53.400 align:middle line:84%
not only can we use
it independently

00:09:53.400 --> 00:09:57.520 align:middle line:84%
of the cranial brain,
but we can tune our heart

00:09:57.520 --> 00:10:00.860 align:middle line:84%
to work with our brain, tune
the neural network of our heart

00:10:00.860 --> 00:10:02.750 align:middle line:90%
to work with our brain.

00:10:02.750 --> 00:10:05.630 align:middle line:84%
Two organs, a single
potent neural network.

00:10:05.630 --> 00:10:08.060 align:middle line:84%
And when we learn to
harmonize that network

00:10:08.060 --> 00:10:10.390 align:middle line:84%
and allow it to serve us
in the way it was intended,

00:10:10.390 --> 00:10:13.410 align:middle line:84%
miraculous-appearing
things happen in the body.

00:10:13.410 --> 00:10:16.480 align:middle line:84%
Which is precisely what happened
with me in my experience,

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:20.610 align:middle line:84%
because I was following the
traditions of our ancestors.

00:10:20.610 --> 00:10:23.757 align:middle line:84%
Those who've come before us
who didn't know the science,

00:10:23.757 --> 00:10:25.340 align:middle line:84%
but they understood
the relationships.

00:10:25.340 --> 00:10:27.550 align:middle line:84%
They didn't use the
words, but they really

00:10:27.550 --> 00:10:29.580 align:middle line:90%
knew how these things work.

00:10:29.580 --> 00:10:33.820 align:middle line:84%
And I was simply following
the harmonization techniques,

00:10:33.820 --> 00:10:36.230 align:middle line:84%
tuning the heart and
the brain together.

00:10:36.230 --> 00:10:39.780 align:middle line:84%
And once that
harmony occurs, it's

00:10:39.780 --> 00:10:41.109 align:middle line:90%
like this signal to your body.

00:10:41.109 --> 00:10:42.650 align:middle line:84%
All of a sudden,
