00:10:42.650 --> 00:10:46.910 align:middle line:84%
1400-plus biochemical
reactions are

00:10:46.910 --> 00:10:49.780 align:middle line:84%
released into the body,
powerful immune response,

00:10:49.780 --> 00:10:52.595 align:middle line:84%
