00:10:52.595 --> 00:10:54.010 align:middle line:90%
But it's all about harmony.

00:10:54.010 --> 00:10:56.650 align:middle line:84%
And it's just from tuning
our heart and our brain.

00:10:56.650 --> 00:10:59.230 align:middle line:84%
It opens the door to
powerful states of intuition,

00:10:59.230 --> 00:11:03.620 align:middle line:84%
