deep states of pre-cognition,

00:11:03.620 --> 00:11:07.340 align:middle line:84%
all of these things from the
single act of harmonizing

00:11:07.340 --> 00:11:09.040 align:middle line:90%
our heart and our brain.

00:11:09.040 --> 00:11:10.560 align:middle line:90%
We call that an altered state.

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:13.970 align:middle line:84%
My sense is it's probably
more the real state,

00:11:13.970 --> 00:11:16.090 align:middle line:84%
and we have strayed
from that, so now it

00:11:16.090 --> 00:11:18.440 align:middle line:84%
appears altered
and foreign to us.

