>>BRADEN: Our
ancestors once again

00:12:30.440 --> 00:12:32.280 align:middle line:84%
had a greater vision
than what we've

00:12:32.280 --> 00:12:33.710 align:middle line:90%
been conditioned to accept.

00:12:33.710 --> 00:12:38.220 align:middle line:84%
