large expanses of time.

00:12:38.220 --> 00:12:40.370 align:middle line:84%
And they looked
at cycles of time,

00:12:40.370 --> 00:12:45.190 align:middle line:84%
because nature works in cycles,
and our bodies work in cycles.

00:12:45.190 --> 00:12:48.550 align:middle line:84%
