00:12:52.970 --> 00:12:54.270 align:middle line:90%
And some we're less aware of.

00:12:54.270 --> 00:12:57.400 align:middle line:84%
And some cover huge
expanses of time

00:12:57.400 --> 00:13:00.040 align:middle line:84%
so long that no one
in a single lifetime

00:13:00.040 --> 00:13:01.360 align:middle line:90%
remembers those things.

00:13:01.360 --> 00:13:03.422 align:middle line:90%
Climate is among those things.

00:13:03.422 --> 00:13:04.630 align:middle line:90%
So I want to be really clear.

00:13:04.630 --> 00:13:07.720 align:middle line:84%
We definitely, I
