we share medical
supplies in times

00:16:33.140 --> 00:16:36.590 align:middle line:84%
of crisis with our brothers and
sisters throughout the world.

00:16:36.590 --> 00:16:39.670 align:middle line:84%
It's all been based in this
language of separation.

00:16:39.670 --> 00:16:42.080 align:middle line:10%
In the story of
separation, we've

00:16:42.080 --> 00:16:44.700 align:middle line:10%
been conditioned to ask
