in ways that we simply
didn't allow ourselves

00:17:08.812 --> 00:17:10.770 align:middle line:84%
to see in the past, that
we're deeply connected

00:17:10.770 --> 00:17:12.300 align:middle line:84%
to our own bodies,
to one another,

00:17:12.300 --> 00:17:14.089 align:middle line:90%
and to the world around us.

00:17:14.089 --> 00:17:17.089 align:middle line:84%
And with that knowledge it
means that the question we've

00:17:17.089 --> 00:17:19.150 align:middle line:90%
asked in the past must change.

00:17:19.150 --> 00:17:21.740 align:middle line:84%
Rather than asking, what can I
get from the world that exists?

00:17:21.740 --> 00:17:24.829 align:middle line:84%
The new question now
