00:17:24.829 --> 00:17:25.743 align:middle line:10%
What can I share?

00:17:25.743 --> 00:17:26.659 align:middle line:10%
What can I contribute?

00:17:26.659 --> 00:17:30.020 align:middle line:10%
What can I offer to the
world that's emerging?

00:17:30.020 --> 00:17:34.080 align:middle line:10%
And the way you answer this
question changes everything.

00:17:34.080 --> 00:17:37.890 align:middle line:84%
If you find yourself
in a job or a career

00:17:37.890 --> 00:17:40.990 align:middle line:84%
that simply doesn't
make sense any longer.

00:17:40.990 --> 00:17:43.600 align:middle line:84%
Entire industries now are
collapsing and disappearing,

00:17:43.600 --> 00:17:46.610 align:middle line:84%
and people are left wondering,
what am I going to do next?

00:17:46.610 --> 00:17:49.799 align:middle line:84%
The way you answer this
question holds the key

00:17:49.799 --> 00:17:51.590 align:middle line:84%
and makes the difference
between you simply

00:17:51.590 --> 00:17:54.800 align:middle line:84%
surviving in the times
that we're living now--

00:17:54.800 --> 00:17:58.800 align:middle line:84%
